<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#667eea">
  <meta name="description" content="Free QR code coat check system for events. NFC ready. Create your temporary wardrobe management system in 30 seconds.">
  <title>Garderobe Digital - QR Code Coat Check for Events</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: #fff;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 20px;
      opacity: 0.95;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 20px 50px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      color: #667eea;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      margin-bottom: 50px;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
      background: #fff;
    }

    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 50px;
    }

    .feature {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 25px 20px;
    }

    .feature-icon {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .feature-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .feature-desc {
      font-size: 12px;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .info-section {
      margin-top: 60px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .info-title {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .info-item {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding-left: 30px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .info-item::before {
      content: "‚úì";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #10b981;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 50px;
      opacity: 0.8;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    }

    .version {
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-size: 12px;
      opacity: 0.6;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      h1 {
        font-size: 32px;
      }

      .tagline {
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .features {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">üß•</div>
    <h1>Garderobe Digital</h1>
    <div class="tagline">QR Code Coat Check for Events</div>

    <a href="/new" class="cta-button">Create New Event</a>

    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">‚ö°</div>
        <div class="feature-title">30-Second Setup</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">No registration required</div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">üì±</div>
        <div class="feature-title">NFC Ready</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">Works with any phone</div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">üîí</div>
        <div class="feature-title">Secure Tokens</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">Cryptographically safe</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-section">
      <div class="info-title">How It Works</div>

      <div class="info-item">
        <strong>Create your event</strong> - Get unique URLs for guests and staff in seconds
      </div>

      <div class="info-item">
        <strong>Write guest URL to NFC tags</strong> - Place tags at your coat check counter
      </div>

      <div class="info-item">
        <strong>Guests tap to get tickets</strong> - Digital ticket with QR code appears instantly
      </div>

      <div class="info-item">
        <strong>Staff scan QR codes</strong> - Check in coats, assign locations, manage retrieval
      </div>

      <div class="info-item">
        <strong>Auto-deletes after 24 hours</strong> - Zero cleanup, zero maintenance
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        Open Source ‚Ä¢ <a href="https://github.com/wehnsdaefflae/garderobe" target="_blank">GitHub</a> ‚Ä¢
        Built in Berlin with ‚ù§Ô∏è for the events community
      </p>
      <p class="version">v<%= version %></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
